text: Axakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Usman-Tashlinsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 22 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Yermekeyevo, 2 km from Usman-Tashly. == References == 48 °F (9 °C), Wind S at 10 mph (16 km/h), 86% Humidity.
